snippet.title: Trailer Tamarindos Freaking Dinner
snippet.description: Tamarindos Freaking Dinner™; the spiritual successor of Baobabs Mausoleum™. The second game of the "Jacob Jazz´s Treelogy". A mix between A 90´s sitcom, Luigi´s Mansion, Metroid Prime & the tabletop game Clue!
